                    <p class="about-story">
                        Courtney Sanders has always had a sweet tooth and an appreciation for a delicious slice of moist cake!
                        She picked up baking as a hobby and soon found herself constantly baking for friends and family.
                        In 2017, during college, she started Courtney Cakes as a home-based, cupcake catering business.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about-story">
                        Today, Courtney Cakes specializes in yummy gourmet cupcakes to enjoy for birthdays, weddings, showers and many other special events. 
                        Courtney prides herself in using the freshest ingredients to create cupcakes, and her delectable, smooth buttercream and cream cheese frostings add the perfect finishing touch. 
                    </p>
